t-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">visual timers</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;"> so she sees how long she needs to focus.</span></p></li></ul><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-top:14pt;margin-bottom:14pt;"><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">✅ </span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">Balance Active &amp; Calm Time</span></p><ul style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-inline-start:48px;"><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type:disc;font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;" aria-level="1"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-top:14pt;margin-bottom:0pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">Let her </span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">move between tasks</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">—jumping, stretching, or dancing can help reset her focus.</span></p></li><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type:disc;font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;" aria-level="1"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:14pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">Introduce </span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">mindfulness activities</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;"> like deep breathing or storytelling before quiet activities.</span></p></li></ul><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-top:14pt;margin-bottom:14pt;"><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">✅ </span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">Praise Effort, Not Just Results</span></p><p><span id="docs-internal-guid-e460dae2-7fff-eab2-5c04-c1e161c7ad83"></span></p><ul style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-inline-start:48px;"><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type:disc;font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;" aria-level="1"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-top:14pt;margin-bottom:0pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">Say, “I love how you focused for 6 minutes today!”</span></p></li><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type:disc;font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;" aria-level="1"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:14pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">Celebrate small wins to boost motivation.</span></p></li></ul>	t	2025-02-28 12:46:04.403	2025-03-08 14:20:12.543	2025-02-28 12:46:04.333	\N	1	en	2025-02-28 12:46:04.231	f	4	60	202	Helping Your Child Improve Focus & Attention
14	<h2 data-start="118" data-end="189" class=""></h2><h6 style="margin-left: 25px;" class=""><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">Ever been in the middle of your child’s meltdown and\nthought, </span><i><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">“What on earth is going on?”</span></i><br><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">\nYeah. Us too.</span><o:p></o:p></p><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">\n\n</span><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">Kids don’t come preloaded with the ability to say, “I’m\nfeeling overwhelmed because I didn’t get what I expected.”</span><br><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">\n(Imagine if they did, though? </span><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">😅</span><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">)</span><o:p></o:p></p><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">\n\n</span><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">But here’s the good news: </span><b><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">emotional intelligence</span></b><span style="font-family: Tahoma;"> can\nbe taught—and it doesn’t require fancy lessons or parenting degrees.</span><o:p></o:p></p><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">\n\n</span><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="text-indent: -0.25in; margin-left: 25px;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;\nmso-bidi-font-weight:bold"><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">o</span><span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma;">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><b><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">What\nIs Emotional Intelligence, Anyway?</span><o:p></o:p></b></p><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">\n\n</span><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 25px;"><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">In simple terms, it’s the ability to:</span><o:p></o:p></p><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">\n\n</span><ul style="margin-top:0in" type="disc"><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">\n </span></ul><p style="margin-left: 25px;"><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">Understand\n     your own feelings</span><o:p></o:p></p><p style="margin-left: 25px;"><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">Recognize\n     others’ emotions</span><o:p></o:p></p><p style="margin-left: 25px;"><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">Handle\n     big emotions without losing control</span><o:p></o:p></p><ul style="margin-top:0in" type="disc"><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">\n \n </span></ul><ul style="margin-top:0in" type="disc"><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">\n</span></ul><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">\n\n</span><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 25px;"><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">The earlier kids start learning these skills, the better\nthey get at handling </span><b><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">frustration, friendship, and failure</span></b><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">—stuff they’ll\nface every day.</span><o:p></o:p></p><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">\n\n</span><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="text-indent: -0.25in; margin-left: 25px;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;\nmso-bidi-font-weight:bold"><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">o</span><span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma;">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><b><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">It\nStarts With Naming Feelings</span><o:p></o:p></b></p><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">\n\n</span><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 25px;"><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">If kids can’t name it, they can’t tame it.</span><br><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">\nTry using real words when emotions come up:</span><o:p></o:p></p><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">\n\n</span><ul style="margin-top:0in" type="disc"><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">\n </span></ul><p style="margin-left: 25px;"><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">“You\n     look really frustrated right now.”</span><o:p></o:p></p><p style="margin-left: 25px;"><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">“That\n     made you sad, huh?”</span><o:p></o:p></p><p style="margin-left: 25px;"><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">“You’re\n     feeling proud—look at that smile!”</span><o:p></o:p></p><ul style="margin-top:0in" type="disc"><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">\n \n </span></ul><ul style="margin-top:0in" type="disc"><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">\n</span></ul><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">\n\n</span><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 25px;"><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">This teaches them that </span><b><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">emotions are normal</span></b><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">, not scary\nor “bad.”</span><o:p></o:p></p><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">\n\n</span><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="text-indent: -0.25in; margin-left: 25px;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;\nmso-bidi-font-weight:bold"><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">o</span><span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma;">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><b><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">Play\nYour Way Through It</span><o:p></o:p></b></p><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">\n\n</span><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 25px;"><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">You don’t need to sit them down for a lecture. Play helps:</span><o:p></o:p></p><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">\n\n</span><ul style="margin-top:0in" type="disc"><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">\n </span></ul><p style="margin-left: 25px;"><b><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">Feeling\n     flashcards</span></b><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">: Faces and names to match the emotion</span><o:p></o:p></p><p style="margin-left: 25px;"><b><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">Storytime\n     swaps</span></b><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">: “How do you think that character felt?”</span><o:p></o:p></p><p style="margin-left: 25px;"><b><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">Role-playing\n     games</span></b><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">: Practice what to do when someone’s upset</span><span style="color: var(--bs-heading-color,inherit); font-size: 1rem; background-color: var(--bs-card-bg); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align); font-family: Tahoma;">&nbsp;</span></p><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">\n\n</span><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="text-indent: -0.25in; margin-left: 25px;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;\nmso-bidi-font-weight:bold"><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">o</span><span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma;">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><b><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">Model\nIt (Even When It's Hard)</span><o:p></o:p></b></p><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">\n\n</span><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 25px;"><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">Kids learn by watching. If you stay calm when you’re\nupset—or if you lose it and then talk about it afterward—they’ll learn it’s\nokay to have emotions </span><b><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">and</span></b><span style="font-family: Tahoma;"> how to recover.</span><o:p></o:p></p><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">\n\n</span><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 25px;"><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">Try saying things like:</span><o:p></o:p></p><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">\n\n</span><ul style="margin-top:0in" type="disc"><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">\n </span></ul><p style="margin-left: 25px;"><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">“I was\n     really annoyed earlier. I took a deep breath, and now I feel better.”</span><o:p></o:p></p><p style="margin-left: 25px;"><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">“I\n     felt hurt when that happened. Talking about it helped.”</span><o:p></o:p></p><ul style="margin-top:0in" type="disc"><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">\n </span></ul><ul style="margin-top:0in" type="disc"><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">\n</span></ul><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">\n\n</span><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="text-indent: -0.25in; margin-left: 25px;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;\nmso-bidi-font-weight:bold"><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">o</span><span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma;">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><b><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">Quick\nWins for Emotional Growth</span><o:p></o:p></b></p><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">\n\n</span><ul style="margin-top:0in" type="disc"><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">\n </span></ul><p style="margin-left: 25px;"><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">Validate\n     before solving: “Yeah, that was hard,” instead of “You’re fine.”</span><o:p></o:p></p><p style="margin-left: 25px;"><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">Create\n     a calm-down corner or safe space.</span><o:p></o:p></p><p style="margin-left: 25px;"><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">Use\n     bedtime as talk-time: Kids often open up when the lights are low.</span><o:p></o:p></p><ul style="margin-top:0in" type="disc"><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">\n \n </span></ul><ul style="margin-top:0in" type="disc"><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">\n</span></ul><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">\n\n</span><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">Your child doesn’t need to be perfect—they just need to know\nit’s okay to feel all the feels.</span><br><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">\nWhen you make space for emotions, you give them a </span><b><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">superpower</span></b><span style="font-family: Tahoma;"> that lasts\nfor life.</span><o:p></o:p></p><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">\n\n</span><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">And you?</span><br><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">\nYou’re already doing better than you think.</span><o:p></o:p></p><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">\n\n</span><p class="MsoNormal"><o:p><span style="font-family: Tahoma;">&nbsp;</span></o:p></p></h6><p class="">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n</p><p class="MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>	t	2025-02-28 14:55:35.255	2025-04-09 20:25:24.683	2025-02-28 14:55:35.081	\N	1	en	2025-